77
00:04:38,027 --> 00:04:41,197
<i>has a characteristic
kind of lettering on it</i>

78
00:04:41,489 --> 00:04:43,032
<i>that's really quite beautiful.</i>

79
00:04:43,992 --> 00:04:47,954
<i>I was thinking that there might be
something in this whole milieu</i>

80
00:04:48,037 --> 00:04:50,290
<i>that could inspire a family of typefaces. </i>

81
00:04:51,541 --> 00:04:53,293
This thing is great. This is like a...

82
00:04:53,710 --> 00:04:56,921
heavy metal sans-serif
with these sort of hexagonal,

83
00:04:57,005 --> 00:04:59,841
bone-shaped figures
