84
00:05:00,341 --> 00:05:02,844
But I really love these kinds of things
that are so much simpler.

85
00:05:02,927 --> 00:05:06,222
I mean, this is a very boxy,
almost octagonal

86
00:05:06,472 --> 00:05:08,558
form of lettering and numbering.

87
00:05:08,641 --> 00:05:10,184
And you see the same kind of thing here,

88
00:05:10,268 --> 00:05:12,478
but a little more sophistication
in this one.

89
00:05:13,896 --> 00:05:16,107
<i>Michael Bierut once described what I do.</i>

90
00:05:16,316 --> 00:05:20,111
<i>He compared it to the archaeologist
