92
00:05:23,072 --> 00:05:25,742
<i>A lot of what I do is finding those bones</i>

93
00:05:25,908 --> 00:05:28,953
<i>and trying to imagine
what kind of creature they came from.</i>

94
00:05:29,620 --> 00:05:31,539
[ticking]

95
00:05:37,962 --> 00:05:40,923
Type design is different now
than when I started doing this.

96
00:05:41,257 --> 00:05:42,925
To be a type designer was to be a freak.

97
00:05:44,218 --> 00:05:47,764
I always dreaded
the conversation on an airline

98
00:05:47,847 --> 00:05:50,016
